HEADWORD: Rajah
<hw>Ra"jah</hw> <pr>(r⟦aum⟧"j⟦aum⟧ ⟦or⟧ r⟦amac⟧"j⟦adot⟧)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Hind. <ets>r⟦amac⟧j⟦amac⟧</ets>, Skr.
